incident_updates.body:
The affected servers are gradually coming back online. 
Our teams continue to work to resolve this incident.
We are continuing to work on a fix for this issue.

Start time : 21/07/2024 22:45 UTC Service impact : Some servers in the following racks R713A01, R713A08, R713A07, R713A11, R715A01, R717A02, R713A03, R717A09 and R713A06 are no longer responding. Root cause : Incident due to disjunction. Ongoing actions : Our technical teams are working on a fix.

As part of our continuous improvement plan, a maintenance is scheduled on our network infrastructure. Start time : 24/07/2024 02:00 UTC End time : 24/07/2024 03:00 UTC Service impact : vRack network will be unavailable during the maintenance for servers without LACP configured which are located in rack BHS0815A02C. Service improvement : Following our continuous improvement policy, we will be doing a maintenance on a network equipment. Thank you for your understanding.

As part of our continuous improvement plan, a maintenance is scheduled on our network infrastructure. Start time : 25/07/2024 02:00 UTC End time : 25/07/2024 03:00 UTC Service impact : vRack network will be unavailable during the maintenance for servers in rack G243A04. Service improvement : Following our continuous improvement policy, we will be doing a maintenance on a network equipment. Thank you for your understanding.
We will be undergoing scheduled maintenance during this time.
Scheduled maintenance is currently in progress. We will provide updates as necessary.
Maintenance will begin as scheduled in 60 minutes.

As part of our continuous improvement plan, a maintenance is scheduled on our network infrastructure. Start time : 12/08/2024 00:30 UTC End time : 12/08/2024 01:30 UTC Service impact : Public network will be unavailable during the maintenance for servers in rack 040818A. Service improvement : Following our continuous improvement policy, we will be doing a maintenance on a network equipment. Thank you for your understanding.

As part of our continuous improvement plan, maintenance is scheduled on our Bare Metal offer. Start time : 12/08/2024 10:00 UTC End time : 12/08/2024 11:30 UTC Service impact : Public network will be temporarily unavailable for servers in rack BHS0810B04A. Service improvement : Following our continuous improvement policy of our network infrastructure, we will be doing a maintenance on a network equipment. Thank you for your understanding.

As part of our continuous improvement plan, maintenance is scheduled on our API. The 27th of August 2024, the following API call will be definitely removed: GET /dedicated/server/{serviceName}/install/templateCapabilities Start time : 27/08/2024 08:30 UTC End time : 27/08/2024 08:45 UTC Service impact : None Service improvement : This API call was previously useful for old Windows OS installers that were not compatible with installation on another diskgroup on servers with multiple diskgroups. Since then all OSes can be installed on any diskgroup. Thank you for your understanding.
